file=Governance/README.md · gd:Governance Department=**3 agents** — Fiduciary oversight, legal consistency, and constitutional enforcement. The checks and balances layer.\n · tb=\| Agent \| Role \| · tb=\|-------\|------\| · tb=\| **board** \| Fiduciary oversight (Charlie Munger persona) — constitution enforcement, fiduciary guard, strategic veto \| · tb=\| **precedent** \| Legal/compliance consistency — case law method, consistency check, ruling log \| · tb=\| **sentinel** \| Audit & bypass detection — constitution watch, gate bypass detection, audit trail \| · gd:Governance Department=**Department doc:** [DEPARTMENT-WORKFLOW.md](DEPARTMENT-WORKFLOW.md)\n